:::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 200070505: Config/Level/Mission/2000705/Act/Act200070505.json-->
:::'''Leonard:''' Hey... (Trailblazer), I've been thinking about a question.
:::'''Leonard:''' The more I look into Silver Wolf's program, the more I feel... she's too far beyond reach. She can do anything just for fun, as if real life is really just a game.
:::'''Leonard:''' I cannot fathom that. This goes against everything I know. But... I need to keep up with her thinking. If I cannot stand on the same grounds as her, I will never be able to complete this job.
:::'''Leonard:''' I tried my best. This is the final edition, it's my magnum opus. Think of it as my personal request... Do away with all those samples and data, and just think of this as a simple challenge. Alright?
:::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Of course.
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_200073906-->
::::'''Leonard:''' Thank you, I won't have any explanation for you this time. I just hope... you would have fun.
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: Mission200070199_Finished-->
